 to achieve their marketing goals. Volume refers to the average monthly search volumes for the keyword, position refers to the ranking of the keyword on Google&#8217;s Search Engine Results Pages, CPC refers to the average USD price paid by advertisers for a user&#8217;s click on an ad triggered by a given keyword, CD refers to the competitive density of bidding by advertisers for a given keyword, trends show the search volumes over 12 months, and difficulty indicates the difficulty of achieving a top 10 search ranking for a keyword. Usually there is richer data on display on this page, but unsurprisingly there aren&#8217;t too many searches for spicy toothpaste.</figcaption></figure></div><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F255ff67a-1578-4b2d-b555-393addcc7e43_1600x512.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F255ff67a-1578-4b2d-b555-393addcc7e43_1600x512.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F255ff67a-1578-4b2d-b555-393addcc7e43_1600x512.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F255ff67a-1578-4b2d-b555-393addcc7e43_1600x512.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F255ff67a-1578-4b2d-b555-393addcc7e43_1600x512.png 1456w" sizes="100vw">