 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">The CMP even helps customers come up with content ideas based on their keyword portfolios. For instance, creating these kinds of articles would be very useful for our hypothetical spicy toothpaste brand to attract potential buyers.</figcaption></figure></div><p>Once the customers have figured out their content strategy, they can move on to the creation phase. This phase begins with the selection of a content type. Popular content types include SEO-friendly blogs, in-depth blogs, and web-page translations. Each of these content types has its own creation questionnaire and delivery workflow.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1f0e7875-59a7-44f2-8c51-477efc5cf0e6_3430x808.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1f0e7875-59a7-44f2-8c51-477efc5cf0e6_3430x808.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1f0e7875-59a7-44f2-8c51-477efc5cf0e6_3430x808.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1f0e7875-59a7-44f2-8c51-477efc5cf0e6_3430x808.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaw